---
---

<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="section-inner stealth-inner">
    <div class="stealth-text">
      <p class="section-label">By design</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built to be invisible</h2>
      <p>
        The extension installs as "Clipboard Manager" with a generic clipboard icon. The toolbar
        popup is a fully functional clipboard history tool. Nothing about the store listing hints
        at what is underneath.
      </p>
      <p>
        The chat button is 20 pixels wide, semi-transparent at 60% opacity by default, and
        positioned at the edge of the viewport. The chatbox itself can be dialed down to 5%
        opacity. Every element uses z-index layering to avoid interfering with page content.
      </p>
      <p>
        Keyboard shortcuts (Alt+C, Alt+Q) let you operate without clicking anything. The
        manifest, description, and declared permissions all read like a standard text utility.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="stealth-visual">
      <div class="stealth-manifest">
        <div class="manifest-header">manifest.json</div>
        <pre><code>{`{
  "manifest_version": 2,
  "name": "Clipboard Manager",
  "version": "4.2.2",
  "description": "Simple clipboard history
    and text snippets manager",
  "browser_specific_settings": {
    "gecko": {
      "id": "clipboard-manager@tools.browser"
    }
  },
  "permissions": [
    "activeTab",
    "storage",
    "tabs"
  ]
}`}</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stealth-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: center; }
  .stealth-text p { font-size: 14px; color: #52525b; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .stealth-text p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .stealth-manifest { border: 1px solid #e4e4e7; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; background: #fafafa; }
  .manifest-header {
    padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: #71717a;
    background: #f4f4f5; border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e7;
    font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", "Fira Code", monospace;
  }
  .stealth-manifest pre { padding: 16px; margin: 0; overflow-x: auto; }
  .stealth-manifest code { font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", "Fira Code", monospace; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #3f3f46; }

  @media (max-width: 960px) { .stealth-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; } }
</style>
